<!DOCTYPE html>
<html ng-app="ravada.app">
%= include 'bootstrap/header'
<body id="page-top" data-spy="scroll" data-target=".navbar-fixed-top" role="document">
    <div id="wrapper">
    %= include 'bootstrap/navigation'
    <div id="page-wrapper">

        <!--BASES AND DOMAINS LIST-->

            <div class="page-header">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h2 class="text-center"><%=l 'Requirements' %></h2>
						<i class="fab fa-linux fa-3x " aria-hidden="true"> GNU/Linux</i>
                        <ul>
                            <li><b>RDP:</b>
                                <%=l 'Install remmina with RDP plugin to view Windows and Linux virtual machines with RDP.' %>
                                <pre>sudo apt-get install remmina remmina-plugin-rdp</pre>
                            </li>

                            <li>
                                <b>Spice:</b> <%=l 'For Spice redirection you will need to install' %><a target=_blank href="https://virt-manager.org/download.html"> VirtViewer<i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a> <%=l 'in your computer.' %><br>
                                <%=l 'Search in your distro, e.g. in Debian/Ubuntu with' %>
                                <pre>sudo apt-get install virt-viewer</pre>
                                <%=l 'Another tool that works well with SPICE is remmina.' %>
                                <pre>sudo apt-get install remmina</pre>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <i class="fab fa-windows fa-3x" aria-hidden="true"> Microsoft Windows </i>&copy;
                        <ul>
                            <li><b>RDP:</b>
                                <%=l 'RDP works out of the box because the client is installed by default.' %>
                            </li>
                            <li><b>SPICE:</b>
                                <%=l 'You will need to install' %>
						            <a target=_blank href="https://virt-manager.org/download.html">VirtViewer<i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i> </a>

                                    <%=l 'and USB drivers (' %><a href="https://www.spice-space.org/download/windows/usbdk/UsbDk_1.0.22_x64.msi">64 <i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i> </a><%=l 'or' %><a href="https://www.spice-space.org/download/windows/usbdk/UsbDk_1.0.22_x86.msi"> 32 <i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i> </a><%=l 'bits) in your computer.' %>

                                <p><%=l 'Be aware that in Windows, Spice redirection is not automatic. It is necessary to associate protocol with the app.' %><br>
                                <%=l 'To make this possible, copy the content of' %><a target=_blank href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/UPC/ravada/gh-pages/docs/docs/spice.reg"> spice.reg <i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i></a> <%=l 'to an ASCII file and save it with a .reg extension, then execute the file.' %><br>
                                <%=l 'Please, make sure you have the right path and release, according to your PC configuration.' %>
                                <p><%=l 'For more information, check' %> <a target=_blank href="http://ravada.readthedocs.io/en/latest/docs/windows_clients.html"><%=l 'the Windows Clients documentation' %></a>.
                            </li>
                        </ul>

                        <i class="fab fa-apple fa-3x " aria-hidden="true"> macOS</i>&copy;
                        <ul>
                            <li><b>RDP:</b>
                                <%=l 'RDP works out of the box because the client is installed by default.' %>
                            </li>
                            <li><b>SPICE:</b>
                                <%=l 'Follow these steps for Spice client setup' %> <a target=_blank href="https://ravada.readthedocs.io/en/latest/docs/mac_clients.html">link <i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </div>
    </div>
%= include 'bootstrap/scripts'
%= include $footer
</body>
</html>
